      • getAtkCtrlListenerKey

        public static String getAtkCtrlListenerKey(int controllerPort,
                           int buttonNum,
                           boolean pressed)
        Builds a string for the AttackPad controller listeners.
        Parameters:
        controllerPort - the port number of the controller
        buttonNum - the button number pressed
        pressed - true if down, false if up
        Returns:
        a listener for ListenerManager which AttackControl will trigger
